'''''De Voortrekkers''''' ni film idafite amajwi yasohotse 1916 yamenyakanye nka filime ya mbere muri   [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . <ref>[https://www.africa-in-motion.org.uk/resources/africas-lost-classics/exhibition/event/315/ "De Voortrekkers 1916"], Africa in Motion Film Festival, screenings at Filmhouse, Edinburgh, Scotland, 4 November 2017; London Castle Cinema, London, England, 9 December 2017. Film distribution by MNet South Africa, Randburg, South Africa. Retrieved 12 August 2021.</ref> Yakozwe na African Film Productions kandi iyobowe na Harold M<ref>(PDF) A tale of two nations: South Africa, De Voortrekkers and Come See the Bioscope (researchgate.net)</ref>. Shaw, yerekana " Great Trek " ya Boers yo mu myaka ya za 1830, isozwa n’imyidagaduro ya hegemonike y’Intambara y’amaraso yabaye ku ya 16 Ukuboza 1838, igihe Abanyafurika bitwaje intwaro<ref>De Voortrekkers (Winning a Continent) | Kanopy</ref> . yatsinze ibihumbi byinshi Zulus . ''Abakomoka kuri voortrekkers'' bavuga ururimi rw’Ubuholandi cyangwa "abapayiniya" bitabiriye Great Trek bubahaga filime kandi barayikoresha mu kwibuka ibirori<ref>Timeline - The Story of Africa| BBC World Service <nowiki>https://www.bbc.co.uk</nowiki> › worldservice › africa › features</ref>, bikaba bigize igice cy’amakimbirane menshi mu mateka ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>Do white people have a future in South Africa? - BBC News <nowiki>https://www.bbc.com</nowiki> › news › magazine-22554709</ref>. Abanyafurika babigaragaje mu byumba by’ishuri imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo kandi barabigaragaza buri mwaka mu birori mbonezamubano bizihiza isabukuru y'intambara<ref>Martin Puryear, Citizen-Sculptor - The New York Times (nytimes.com)</ref>.

''De Voortrekkers'' yerekanwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo ahitwa Krugersdorp ku ya 14 Ukuboza 1916, hasigaye iminsi ibiri ngo isabukuru y'imyaka 78 imaze ibaye<ref>Voortrekkers (1916) - Africa in Motion Film Festival <nowiki>https://www.africa-in-motion.org.uk</nowiki> › exhibition › event</ref>. Nyuma yaje gukwirakwizwa mu magambo ahinnye muri sinema zo mu [[Bwongereza]], [[Amerika]], [[Kanada]], n'ahandi hanze ya Afurika ku izina rya ''Winning a Continent''<ref>De voortrekkers = Winning a continent (DVD video, 1990s ... <nowiki>http://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › oclc</ref> .  Intertitles zikoreshwa muri firime y'umwimerere no mubisohoka nyuma ikoresha imiterere ya ecran yerekana inyandiko mucyongereza no muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] . <ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j8M5vkqvfug "De Voortrekkers (1916) with new orchestral score"], 19:52 segment of film with added music, uploaded by Chris Jeffrey on 23 February 2017 onto [[YouTube]] (San Bruno, California, United States). Retrieved 12 August 2021.</ref>
